<br />
If they want to keep the old content people haven't cleared yet relevant, they should make the tokens that let you roll again for loot in the old raids (which they said would be drops in the new raid, right?) be used to buy upgrades to the old gear instead of rolling for it so you can bring the old raid pieces up to the ilvl of the new but only if you're doing the new content too.</blockquote>
